quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,Nditsuba khulukulu lwa Tur
  52,2,Nende khushitabu shiahandikwa
  52,3,Khuliseelo liabambulwa
  52,4,Nende khunzu yombakhwa
  52,5,Nende khushitsafu shiachingulwa
  52,6,Nende khunyanza yetsula
  52,7,Toto eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shilibaho
  52,8,Abulaho ulishikalila
  52,9,Inyanga yelikulu lilirenga okhurenga khwene
  52,10,Ne tsingulu lwatsilikulukha bukulukha
  52,11,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubayingani
  52,12,Balia babayanga mumakhuwa kobusilu
  52,13,Inyanga yabaliluumwa mumulilo obutinyu
  52,14,"Baliboolewa mbu: “Kuno niko omulilo kwa mwaingananga.”"
  52,15,Koo buno ni obulosi nohomba shimulolangasa tawe
  52,16,"Injilemwo, mwifwile nohomba mukhaye okhwifwila ninashilala, toto enywe murungungwa kamwakholanga"
  52,17,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda nende mubwokholo
  52,18,"Nibasangalila khuka Nyasaye wabu abahele, ne Nyasaye wabu alibahonokosia khu shinyasio shiomulilo"
  52,19,Lie ne munywe mumwikhoyo khukalia kamwakholanga
  52,20,"Ne baliyekha khubifumbi bwoluyali, bilondokhane khulunyaali, ne khulibabashila Abakhana bomwikulu (Hurul ain)"
  52,21,"Ne balia basuubila mana olwibulo lwabu nilubaloonda khukhusuubila khulibabukanania, ne shikhulibalemilia khubikhole biabu shiosishiosi tawe, buli Omundu alirungwa shiayakhola"
  52,22,Ne khulibametela buli imbia yebiamo nende yeyinyama shingala benya
  52,23,Balihelesaniamwo tsigilasi tsilimwo eshinywebwa shibulamwo eshifwabi nohomba obwonooni
  52,24,"Ne Abakholi babu balibabotokhana, bang’enang’ena opara mbu ebisole bifunikhwe mugilasi"
  52,25,Ne balihengana nibareebana
  52,26,"Baliboola mbu: “Toto efwe khwali khale nabandu befu nikhwaria.”"
  52,27,"Mana Nyasaye nakhukhonya, nakhuhonia okhurulana nende eshinyasio shiomulilo"
  52,28,Toto efwe khwamulanganga Ye yenyene butswa. Toto ye niye omulayi wobukoosia
  52,29,"Kho yitsulisia, ne khutsimbaasi tsia Nyasaye wo sholi Omulosi nohomba Omulalu tawe"
  52,30,"Nohomba boboolanga mbu uno ni omukaasia wetsinyimbo, wakhulindanga lifwa limuulile"
  52,31,"Boola mbu: “Lindilisie toto esie siesi endi halala ninanyu mukhulindilisia.”"
  52,32,"Nohomba amaparo kabu niko kabarumanga kario, nohomba bo ni Abandu abafuru butswa"
  52,33,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “wakasia kano!” halali bo shibasuubilangasa tawe"
  52,34,"Mana barere amakhuwa shinga kano, nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto"
  52,35,"Nohomba shibaalongwa okhurula khu shiosi shiosi tawe, nohomba bo nibo baloonga"
  52,36,Nohomba nibo baloonga likulu nende eshialo? Halali babula obulaamba
  52,37,"Nohomba bali nende libishilo lia Nyasaye wuwo, nohomba nibo bali nobunyali"
  52,38,Nohomba bali netsingasi tsiokhurechelesiakhwo? mana omurechelesi wabu oyo arere ebifune bilolekha
  52,39,Nohomba Nyasaye ali nabakhana nanyu muli nabasiani
  52,40,Nohomba abarebanga bakhurunge nabo bali nende obuleemu bwo murungo oko
  52,41,Nohomba bamanyile akefisa mana bakahandika
  52,42,Nohomba benyanga okhukholela amatemo? Halali balia bakhaya nibo abalenjila mumatemo
  52,43,Nohomba bali nende Nyasaye wundi owulali Nyasaye? Nyasaye nomutswenufu khubia bamutsokasinjia ninaye
  52,44,"Ne nibalolanga lileesi lieshinyasio nilikwa okhurula hekulu, bakhaboolele mbu ni amalesi kachingane"
  52,45,Ne baleshe okhuula lwabalibukaanana nende inyanga yabu yabalisishibwa
  52,46,"Inyanga yamarechekho kabu shikakhabakhoonye shiosi shiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe"
  52,47,"Ne toto balia abakhola amabii, balinyoola eshinyasio shindi shilali shino tawe, ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe"
  52,48,"Ne linda okhubusia khwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, toto ewe oli mutsimoni tsiefu, ne mutswenule khulwokhumwitsomia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olwa oba niwema"
  52,49,Ne eshilo khandi omwitsoomie nende olwe tsing’ining’ini tsitsia